                   <span style="font-family:wfont_73f80c_0daaaaabc4164c2c84a7a57643efc255,wf_0daaaaabc4164c2c84a7a5764,orig_goudy_old_style;">

                        Alenah has turned her natural vocal talents into session recordings for Theme Parks, TV and Radio Commercials, Jingles, Children's Audio Albums, and Television and Radio appearances.
                        <br/>
                        Alenah is a full-time Voice Talent with many top credits to her name. Some of her Clients include: McDonalds, NBC Asia, Google, Verizon, Disney World, PetSmart, Ruby Tequila's, College Loan Corp., Quaker State, Subway Restaurants, Friendly's Restaurants, Wal*Mart, Sea World Orlando, BMW, and more.
                        <br/>
                        She also has a solo and group career as a vocalist and has released a CD of original songs. She has performed live at Walt Disney World in Orlando, Florida; and has been recognized as a top vocalist with national awards.
                        <br/>
                        As a trained Keyboardist, Choreographer, and Professional Singer, Alenah has also performed with multiple music projects from Atlanta, GA., to Washington, DC., and has toured all over the state of Florida. She freelances as a Vocal Coach and works with children who have an interest in music.

               <span style="font-size:18px;">
                <span style="font-family:wfont_73f80c_0daaaaabc4164c2c84a7a57643efc255,wf_0daaaaabc4164c2c84a7a5764,orig_goudy_old_style;">
